    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This *+1 striking shortbow* is a favorite of mage hunters and those who frequently fight enemies who can turn themselves invisible. A creature who is critically hit with a ranged Strike from a dazzling shortbow must succeed at a DC 19 Fortitude save or be dazzled for 1 minute.",
